&lt;li>&lt;a class="link" href="./04-April-2024/2024.04.17.md" >Thursday&lt;/a>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Today at &lt;a class="link" href="The%20Virtues%20Campus.md" >Virtues&lt;/a>, we studied the theology of &lt;a class="link" href="55.58%20Hebrews.md" >Hebrews&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
